, as a recognised technician, you must fulfil certain obligations (= user requirements).</p><p><a href=\"https://www.dev-vlaanderen.be/informatie-over-de-erkenning-als-technicus-voor-klimaatregelingsapparatuur-in-motorvoertuigen\">More info on the obligations for approved technicians for air-conditioning equipment in certain motor vehicles.</a></p>",
