            "en-x-generated": "<p>To be recognised as a training centre, it must comply with:</p><ul><li><a href=\"https://navigator.emis.vito.be/mijn-navigator?woId=36058\">general recognition conditions</a> that apply to all environmental recognitions<ul><li>in the 3 years preceding the application for the Flemish certificate of recognition, the applicant has not received a criminal conviction in a <a href=\"https://www.dev-vlaanderen.be/uw-overheid/verdeling-van-de-bevoegdheden/de-europese-unie-eu-de-europese-economische-ruimte-eer-het-schengengebied-en-de-eurozone\">member state of the European Economic Area</a> for breaches of environmental legislation relating to the use of the recognition</li><li>in the 2 years preceding the application for the Flemish recognition certificate, no recognition with the same object has been withdrawn from the applicant, for violation of the related obligations of that recognition.</li></ul></li><li><strong>special conditions of recognition: </strong><ul><li>have sound procedures to organise examinations</li><li>have suitable technical staff</li><li>set up a regulatory examination jury.</li></ul></li></ul><p>More info on the recognition conditions can be found in <a href=\"https://navigator.emis.vito.be/mijn-navigator?woId=36058\">art. 8 VLAREL (general recognition conditions)</a> and:</p><ul><li><a href=\"https://navigator.emis.vito.be/mijn-navigator?woId=36102&amp;woLang=nl\">Art. 21 VLAREL (special recognition conditions training centre technicians liquid fuel)</a>;</li><li><a href=\"https://navigator.emis.vito.be/mijn-navigator?woId=36103&amp;woLang=nl\">art. 22 VLAREL (special recognition conditions training centre technicians gaseous fuel)</a>;</li><li><a href=\"https://navigator.emis.vito.be/mijn-navigator?woId=36104&amp;woLang=nl\">art. 23 VLAREL (special approval conditions training centre for technicians heating audit)</a>. </li></ul><h3>Period of validity and obligations</h3><p>Recognition is valid for<strong> an indefinite</strong> period. However, a recognised training centre must meet a number of <strong>usage requirements </strong>(=obligations) in order to retain its recognition.</p><p><a href=\"https://www.dev-vlaanderen.be/informatie-voor-opleidingscentra-technici-gasvormige-brandstof-vloeibare-brandstof-of-verwarmingsaudit\">More info on the user requirements for accredited training centres for gaseous fuel technicians, liquid fuel technicians and heating audit technicians</a>. </p>",
