            "en": "<p>The company must pay a one-off fee for handling the application for recognition as a fire protection equipment company.</p><ul><li>In <strong>2021</strong>, the one-off fee is <strong>586 </strong>euro.</li><li>For an application in <strong>2022</strong>, the one-off fee is <strong>606 </strong>euro.</li><li>That amount is index-adjusted every year.</li></ul><p>The recognised fire protection equipment company must pay an <a href=\"https://www.uat-vlaanderen.be/vlarel-retributies\">annual fee</a> for the supervision of the recognition. The recognised fire protection equipment company receives an invoice for this by post at the start of the calendar year:</p><ul><li>In <strong>2022</strong>, the annual fee is <strong>121 </strong>euro.</li><li>That amount is index-adjusted every year.</li></ul>",
